{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":422,"text":"You know, my favorite part of being a dad"},{"time":2952,"text":"is the movies I get to watch."},{"time":6211,"text":"I love sharing my favorite movies with my kids,"},{"time":8092,"text":"and when my daughter was four,"},{"time":10688,"text":"we got to watch \"The Wizard of Oz\" together."},{"time":13578,"text":"It totally dominated her imagination for months."},{"time":16977,"text":"Her favorite character was Glinda, of course."},{"time":20195,"text":"It gave her a great excuse to wear a sparkly dress"},{"time":22255,"text":"and carry a wand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23909,"text":"But you watch that movie enough times,"},{"time":26318,"text":"and you start to realize how unusual it is."},{"time":27751,"text":"Now we live today, and are raising our children,"},{"time":30603,"text":"in a kind of children's-fantasy-spectacular-industrial complex."},{"time":36953,"text":"But \"The Wizard of Oz\" stood alone."},{"time":38698,"text":"It did not start that trend."},{"time":40885,"text":"Forty years later was when the trend really caught on,"},{"time":44307,"text":"with, interestingly, another movie"},{"time":46656,"text":"that featured a metal guy"},{"time":48791,"text":"and a furry guy"},{"time":50175,"text":"rescuing a girl by dressing up as the enemy's guards."},{"time":55386,"text":"Do you know what I'm talking about? (Laughter)"},{"time":57827,"text":"Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59302,"text":"Now, there's a big difference between these two movies,"},{"time":63025,"text":"a couple of really big differences between \"The Wizard of Oz\""},{"time":65062,"text":"and all the movies we watch today."},{"time":65995,"text":"One is there's very little violence in \"The Wizard of Oz.\""},{"time":69300,"text":"The monkeys are rather aggressive, as are the apple trees."},{"time":74545,"text":"But I think if \"The Wizard of Oz\" were made today,"},{"time":78152,"text":"the wizard would say, \"Dorothy, you are the savior of Oz"},{"time":82578,"text":"that the prophecy foretold."},{"time":84340,"text":"Use your magic slippers to defeat"},{"time":86414,"text":"the computer-generated armies of the Wicked Witch.\""},{"time":90027,"text":"But that's not how it happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91679,"text":"Another thing that's really unique about \"The Wizard of Oz\""},{"time":94081,"text":"to me is that all of the most heroic"},{"time":97384,"text":"and wise and even villainous characters"},{"time":100714,"text":"are female."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104226,"text":"Now I started to notice this"},{"time":106340,"text":"when I actually showed \"Star Wars\" to my daughter,"},{"time":109485,"text":"which was years later, and the situation was different."},{"time":112021,"text":"At that point I also had a son."},{"time":115160,"text":"He was only three at the time."},{"time":116887,"text":"He was not invited to the screening. He was too young for that."},{"time":121033,"text":"But he was the second child,"},{"time":122354,"text":"and the level of supervision had plummeted. (Laughter)"},{"time":126127,"text":"So he wandered in,"},{"time":129741,"text":"and it imprinted on him"},{"time":133770,"text":"like a mommy duck does to its duckling,"},{"time":139412,"text":"and I don't think he understands what's going on,"},{"time":143191,"text":"but he is sure soaking in it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146718,"text":"And I wonder what he's soaking in."},{"time":148087,"text":"Is he picking up on the themes of courage"},{"time":150565,"text":"and perseverance and loyalty?"},{"time":152682,"text":"Is he picking up on the fact that Luke"},{"time":155662,"text":"joins an army to overthrow the government?"},{"time":160556,"text":"Is he picking up on the fact that"},{"time":162212,"text":"there are only boys in the universe"},{"time":165315,"text":"except for Aunt Beru, and of course this princess,"},{"time":168504,"text":"who's really cool, but who kind of waits around through most of the movie"},{"time":172954,"text":"so that she can award the hero with a medal and a wink"},{"time":176183,"text":"to thank him for saving the universe, which he does"},{"time":178736,"text":"by the magic that he was born with?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181962,"text":"Compare this to 1939 with \"The Wizard of Oz.\""},{"time":184928,"text":"How does Dorothy win her movie?"},{"time":187557,"text":"By making friends with everybody"},{"time":190507,"text":"and being a leader."},{"time":192284,"text":"That's kind of the world I'd rather raise my kids in --"},{"time":195590,"text":"Oz, right? -- and not the world of dudes fighting,"},{"time":199480,"text":"which is where we kind of have to be."},{"time":201383,"text":"Why is there so much Force -- capital F, Force --"},{"time":205163,"text":"in the movies we have for our kids,"},{"time":206850,"text":"and so little yellow brick road?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":209295,"text":"There is a lot of great writing about the impact"},{"time":212712,"text":"that the boy-violent movie has on girls,"},{"time":216959,"text":"and you should do that reading. It's very good."},{"time":219577,"text":"I haven't read as much on how boys are picking up on this vibe."},{"time":224451,"text":"I know from my own experience that"},{"time":227001,"text":"Princess Leia did not provide the adequate context"},{"time":232626,"text":"that I could have used in navigating the adult world"},{"time":236755,"text":"that is co-ed. (Laughter)"},{"time":241356,"text":"I think there was a first-kiss moment"},{"time":244546,"text":"when I really expected the credits to start rolling"},{"time":247877,"text":"because that's the end of the movie, right?"},{"time":250680,"text":"I finished my quest, I got the girl."},{"time":252977,"text":"Why are you still standing there?"},{"time":256108,"text":"I don't know what I'm supposed to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257553,"text":"The movies are very, very focused on defeating the villain"},{"time":260741,"text":"and getting your reward, and there's not a lot of room"},{"time":263329,"text":"for other relationships and other journeys."},{"time":266220,"text":"It's almost as though if you're a boy,"},{"time":268459,"text":"you are a dopey animal,"},{"time":270540,"text":"and if you are a girl, you should bring your warrior costume."},{"time":275014,"text":"There are plenty of exceptions,"},{"time":277202,"text":"and I will defend the Disney princesses in front of any you."},{"time":282499,"text":"But they do send a message to boys,"},{"time":285551,"text":"that they are not, the boys are not really the target audience."},{"time":288057,"text":"They are doing a phenomenal job of teaching girls"},{"time":290499,"text":"how to defend against the patriarchy,"},{"time":293871,"text":"but they are not necessarily showing boys"},{"time":295836,"text":"how they're supposed to defend against the patriarchy."},{"time":298670,"text":"There's no models for them."},{"time":300810,"text":"And we also have some terrific women"},{"time":304083,"text":"who are writing new stories for our kids,"},{"time":306220,"text":"and as three-dimensional and delightful as Hermione and Katniss are,"},{"time":310962,"text":"these are still war movies."},{"time":313088,"text":"And, of course, the most successful studio of all time"},{"time":317196,"text":"continues to crank out classic after classic,"},{"time":321326,"text":"every single one of them about"},{"time":324070,"text":"the journey of a boy, or a man,"},{"time":327840,"text":"or two men who are friends, or a man and his son,"},{"time":331484,"text":"or two men who are raising a little girl."},{"time":335079,"text":"Until, as many of you are thinking, this year,"},{"time":338819,"text":"when they finally came out with \"Brave.\""},{"time":340545,"text":"I recommend it to all of you. It's on demand now."},{"time":344552,"text":"Do you remember what the critics said when \"Brave\" came out?"},{"time":348446,"text":"\"Aw, I can't believe Pixar made a princess movie.\""},{"time":352854,"text":"It's very good. Don't let that stop you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354975,"text":"Now, almost none of these movies pass the Bechdel Test."},{"time":358867,"text":"I don't know if you've heard of this."},{"time":360053,"text":"It has not yet caught on and caught fire,"},{"time":362875,"text":"but maybe today we will start a movement."},{"time":364956,"text":"Alison Bechdel is a comic book artist,"},{"time":367738,"text":"and back in the mid-'80s, she recorded this conversation"},{"time":372844,"text":"she'd had with a friend about assessing the movies that they saw."},{"time":376418,"text":"And it's very simple. There's just three questions you should ask:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":379404,"text":"Is there more than one character in the movie"},{"time":381914,"text":"that is female who has lines?"},{"time":385515,"text":"So try to meet that bar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388095,"text":"And do these women talk to each other at any point in the movie?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":393755,"text":"And is their conversation about something other than"},{"time":397208,"text":"the guy that they both like? (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400524,"text":"Right? Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":404856,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406681,"text":"Two women who exist and talk to each other about stuff."},{"time":414284,"text":"It does happen. I've seen it,"},{"time":419414,"text":"and yet I very rarely see it in the movies"},{"time":422362,"text":"that we know and love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423529,"text":"In fact, this week I went to see"},{"time":425689,"text":"a very high-quality movie, \"Argo.\""},{"time":429303,"text":"Right? Oscar buzz, doing great at the box office,"},{"time":432962,"text":"a consensus idea of what a quality Hollywood film is."},{"time":437246,"text":"It pretty much flunks the Bechdel test."},{"time":439930,"text":"And I don't think it should, because a lot of the movie,"},{"time":443737,"text":"I don't know if you've seen it, but a lot of the movie"},{"time":445318,"text":"takes place in this embassy where men and women"},{"time":448776,"text":"are hiding out during the hostage crisis."},{"time":451453,"text":"We've got quite a few scenes of the men"},{"time":453342,"text":"having deep, angst-ridden conversations in this hideout,"},{"time":457503,"text":"and the great moment for one of the actresses is"},{"time":461519,"text":"to peek through the door and say, \"Are you coming to bed, honey?\""},{"time":466641,"text":"That's Hollywood for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468642,"text":"So let's look at the numbers."},{"time":471087,"text":"2011, of the 100 most popular movies,"},{"time":474649,"text":"how many of them do you think actually have female protagonists?"},{"time":478894,"text":"Eleven. It's not bad."},{"time":482188,"text":"It's not as many percent as the number of women"},{"time":485883,"text":"we've just elected to Congress, so that's good."},{"time":489009,"text":"But there is a number that is greater than this"},{"time":492013,"text":"that's going to bring this room down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494670,"text":"Last year, The New York Times published a study"},{"time":498332,"text":"that the government had done."},{"time":499991,"text":"Here's what it said."},{"time":501379,"text":"One out of five women in America"},{"time":505595,"text":"say that they have been sexually assaulted some time in their life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":511848,"text":"Now, I don't think that's the fault of popular entertainment."},{"time":515632,"text":"I don't think kids' movies have anything to do with that."},{"time":519915,"text":"I don't even think that"},{"time":521693,"text":"music videos or pornography are really directly related to that,"},{"time":525248,"text":"but something is going wrong,"},{"time":528013,"text":"and when I hear that statistic,"},{"time":531064,"text":"one of the things I think of is"},{"time":533569,"text":"that's a lot of sexual assailants."},{"time":537694,"text":"Who are these guys? What are they learning?"},{"time":541054,"text":"What are they failing to learn?"},{"time":542770,"text":"Are they absorbing the story that"},{"time":544920,"text":"a male hero's job is to defeat the villain with violence"},{"time":549447,"text":"and then collect the reward, which is a woman"},{"time":551980,"text":"who has no friends and doesn't speak?"},{"time":557028,"text":"Are we soaking up that story?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":562233,"text":"You know,"},{"time":564579,"text":"as a parent with the privilege"},{"time":567346,"text":"of raising a daughter"},{"time":569990,"text":"like all of you who are doing the same thing,"},{"time":572859,"text":"we find this world and this statistic very alarming"},{"time":576639,"text":"and we want to prepare them."},{"time":577776,"text":"We have tools at our disposal like \"girl power,\""},{"time":582062,"text":"and we hope that that will help,"},{"time":584796,"text":"but I gotta wonder, is girl power going to protect them"},{"time":588405,"text":"if, at the same time, actively or passively,"},{"time":591003,"text":"we are training our sons to maintain their boy power?"},{"time":595956,"text":"I mean, I think the Netflix queue"},{"time":599354,"text":"is one way that we can do something very important,"},{"time":602610,"text":"and I'm talking mainly to the dads here."},{"time":605665,"text":"I think we have got to show our sons"},{"time":608515,"text":"a new definition of manhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610371,"text":"The definition of manhood is already turning upside down."},{"time":614891,"text":"You've read about how the new economy"},{"time":617022,"text":"is changing the roles of caregiver and wage earner."},{"time":620423,"text":"They're throwing it up in the air."},{"time":622077,"text":"So our sons are going to have to find some way"},{"time":624695,"text":"of adapting to this, some new relationship with each other,"},{"time":627670,"text":"and I think we really have to show them, and model for them,"},{"time":631517,"text":"how a real man"},{"time":635218,"text":"is someone who trusts his sisters"},{"time":638987,"text":"and respects them, and wants to be on their team,"},{"time":642160,"text":"and stands up against the real bad guys,"},{"time":645783,"text":"who are the men who want to abuse the women."},{"time":649639,"text":"And I think our job in the Netflix queue"},{"time":652690,"text":"is to look out for those movies that pass the Bechdel Test,"},{"time":656459,"text":"if we can find them, and to seek out the heroines"},{"time":660740,"text":"who are there,"},{"time":662326,"text":"who show real courage, who bring people together,"},{"time":666115,"text":"and to nudge our sons to identify with those heroines"},{"time":669703,"text":"and to say, \"I want to be on their team,\""},{"time":673188,"text":"because they're going to be on their team."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677770,"text":"When I asked my daughter who her favorite character was in \"Star Wars,\""},{"time":681464,"text":"do you know what she said?"},{"time":683493,"text":"Obi-Wan."},{"time":685996,"text":"Obi-Wan Kenobi and Glinda."},{"time":689893,"text":"What do these two have in common?"},{"time":693360,"text":"Maybe it's not just the sparkly dress."},{"time":695284,"text":"I think these people are experts."},{"time":698911,"text":"I think these are the two people in the movie"},{"time":700437,"text":"who know more than anybody else,"},{"time":702005,"text":"and they love sharing their knowledge with other people"},{"time":705332,"text":"to help them reach their potential."},{"time":708436,"text":"Now, they are leaders."},{"time":710444,"text":"I like that kind of quest for my daughter,"},{"time":712662,"text":"and I like that kind of quest for my son."},{"time":714849,"text":"I want more quests like that."},{"time":716760,"text":"I want fewer quests where my son is told,"},{"time":719360,"text":"\"Go out and fight it alone,\""},{"time":721571,"text":"and more quests where he sees that it's his job to join a team,"},{"time":726776,"text":"maybe a team led by women,"},{"time":730876,"text":"to help other people become better"},{"time":736496,"text":"and be better people,"},{"time":738888,"text":"like the Wizard of Oz."},{"time":741170,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}